{"tid":1374702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何妖仆硬街，咁李薊貽呢？","createTime":"2019-07-27T23:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T23:56:37.000Z","uid":275872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d68aa6c76acc68c546619cd554ab0980bbf62038","tid":1374702,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T23:50:52.000Z","msg":"牛屎佬只係班好食懶做既廢物，何妖搞得掂既。正如，唔通班牛屎又會搞到中聯辦咩，你老幾呀。牛屎佬咁撚叻，尋日又唔出黎見下我地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被指&ldquo;動員&rdquo;元朗暴力中聯辦部長李薊貽閉嘴拒答記者追問<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PBC9cR3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPBC9cR3.jpg&h=d688c921&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被指在一次新界鄉事會議上發言時涉嫌&ldquo;動員&rdquo;元朗周日發生&ldquo;白衣黑幫&rdquo;恐襲事件的中聯辦新界工作部部長李薊貽，昨日（23日）出席一場公開活動中，遭到記者追問時，一直微笑不語，對是否涉及煽動元朗暴力事件的問題，一概閉嘴不答。<br />\n<br />\n在此同時，已有民間團體計畫在7月27日舉行&ldquo;光復元朗&rdquo;遊行，申請遊行的元朗居民鍾健平說，他們要求政府回應&ldquo;7.21元朗恐襲&rdquo;是否一次有大陸人參與的&ldquo;跨境恐怖襲擊&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://amp.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%B0/20190724-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%8B%95%E5%93%A1%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E6%9D%8E%E8%96%8A%E8%B2%BD%E9%96%89%E5%98%B4%E6%8B%92%E7%AD%94%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%BF%BD%E5%95%8F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Famp.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%258F%25B0%2F20190724-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2581%25AF%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%259D%258E%25E8%2596%258A%25E8%25B2%25BD%25E9%2596%2589%25E5%2598%25B4%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25AD%2594%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E5%2595%258F&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F11m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=9ee1b960\" target=\"_blank\">https://amp.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%B0/20190724-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%8B%95%E5%93%A1%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E6%9D%8E%E8%96%8A%E8%B2%BD%E9%96%89%E5%98%B4%E6%8B%92%E7%AD%94%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%BF%BD%E5%95%8F</a>"},{"pid":"7afd90badbeefaf106113e5ac40e70414d79fbe2","tid":1374702,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T23:51:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a9c36afaa43ca32d075436e831f8a0677fe3bc27","tid":1374702,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T23:51:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2839fbcb3856f1411f9ac8e93a1fb76dd0c056f5","tid":1374702,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T23:56:37.000Z","msg":"push"}]}